Police are investigating the fatal shooting of a man at a mosque in Ravensmead. CAPE TOWN - Police are investigating the fatal shooting of a man at a mosque in Ravensmead.The man was gunned down earlier on Friday at the Husami Masjid in York Street.It is unclear what the circumstances are surrounding the shooting.The police's Frederick van Wyk says: We ve opened a murder case for further investigation. We urge those who might have helpful information about the case to contact us. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)